# Plan Execution Rule

**NEVER call `exitplanmode` or begin implementing without explicit user confirmation.**
When a plan is ready, present it and WAIT. Only proceed when the user says something like "go", "looks good", "do it", or equivalent. Do not infer confirmation from the content of the request.

